content.body:
### Shop 235/65R17 Tire Size 235/65R17 tires are a quickly growing size in the U.S. largely because they’re used on a wide variety of CUVs, SUVs, and minivans. Vehicles such as the Chrysler Pacifica, Ford Bronco Sport, Honda CR-V, Hyundai Santa Fe, Jaguar E-Pace, Kia Sorento, and Toyota Sienna all use 235/65R17 tires on select models, and a brand new version of one might come with a set of Yokohama AVID S34RV,[Falken Wildpeak A/T3W](https://simpletire.com/brands/falken-tires/wildpeak-a-t3w), Bridgestone Ecopia H/L 422 Plus, Nexen Roadian GTX, Goodyear Eagle F1 Asymmetric SUV AT, Kumho Crugen Premium KL33, or Firestone FT140 tires attached as it rolls out of the factory. Popular vehicles: 2004-2008 and 2017-2021 Chrysler Pacifica
2021 Ford Bronco Sport
2017-2021 Honda CR-V
2010-2012 and 2019-2021 Hyundai Santa Fe
2018-2019 Jaguar E-Pace
2011-2021 Kia Sorento
2021 Toyota Sienna Do you drive a minivan like the Chrysler Pacifica, Toyota Sienna, or Kia Carnival? Minivans are often paired with all-season tires thanks to their ability to perform in dry, wet, and light winter weather conditions, and great 235/65R17 options for a minivan include the Michelin Latitude Tour HP,[Continental TrueContact Tour](https://simpletire.com/brands/continental-tires/truecontact-tour), Bridgestone DriveGuard, and Kumho Crugen HT51. CUV and SUV specific tires are a newer entry into the tire market, but there are plenty of great options currently available. Check out the [Pirelli Scorpion Verde All Season Plus II](https://simpletire.com/brands/pirelli-tires/scorpion-verde-all-season-plus-ii), Yokohama Geolandar CV G058, Falken Ziex CT60 A/S, or Hankook Dynapro HP2 (RA33) if you drive a CR-V, Santa Fe, Sorento, or other CUV or SUV and want a 235/65R17 tire that’s built to handle your ride’s heavier weight and higher center of gravity. You likely want to drive off-road from time to time if you drive a Ford Bronco, so finding a tire that performs well on any terrain becomes a must. All-terrain tires are built for the drivers who want to take their ride on- and off-road, and the [Toyo Open Country A/T III](https://simpletire.com/brands/toyo-tires/open-country-a-t-iii), Falken Wildpeak A/T Trail, Nokian Rotiiva AT, and Atturo Trail Blade X/T are all great options for drivers who want to conquer any terrain. Whether you drive a Toyota Sienna, Honda CR-V, Ford Bronco Sport, or something else, SimpleTire has a set of 235/65R17 tires that meets your needs at a great price!
